:: Widgets Hospital [widget]
<<widget "harper_intro">>
	<<if $hospitalintro isnot 1>>
		<<npc Harper>><<person1>>You don't have to wait long. A <<personsimple>> wearing a white medical coat and carrying a clipboard emerges from an adjacent room and beckons you over.
		<br><br>

		<<if $hospitalintro isnot 0>>
			It's the doctor from the farm. The one who experimented on you. You hesitate, but walk over to <<him>>. You're in a busy hospital now, not an isolated farm.
		<</if>>

		<<He>> smiles at you. "Hello, I'm Doctor Harper," <<he>> says.

		<<if $hospitalintro is 0>>
			<<He>> brushes <<his>> blond fringe away from <<his>> eyes. <<He>> looks young for a doctor, can't be older than 25. You enter <<his>> office and take a seat.
		<<else>>
			There's no recognition on <<his>> face. You enter <<his>> office and take a seat.
		<</if>>

		<<set $hospitalintro to 1>>
	<<elseif $hospitalintro is "party">>
		<<set $hospitalintro to 1>>
		<<npc Harper>><<person1>>
		You don't have to wait long. A <<personsimple>> wearing a white medical coat and carrying a clipboard emerges from an adjacent room and beckons you over.
		<br><br>

		It's the doctor from the party at Avery's mansion. "Hello, I'm Doctor Harper." <<His>> face alights with recognition. "Aha. Avery's partner. I hope <<nnpc_he Avery>>'s well." You enter <<his>> office and take a seat.
		<br><br>
	<<else>>
		<<npc Harper>><<person1>>You don't have to wait long. Doctor Harper emerges from <<his>> office and beckons you over. You follow <<him>> in and take a seat.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</widget>>

:: Pharmacy Condoms Price [widget]
<<widget condomsPrice>>
	<<if _args[0] lte 50>>
		<<set _price to _args[0] * 6000>>
	<<elseif _args lte 100>>
		<<set _price to 50 * 6000 + (_args[0] - 50) * 6000 * .98>>
	<<else>>
		<<set _price to 50 * 6000 + 50 * 6000 * .98 + (_args[0] - 100) * 6000 * .95>>
	<</if>>
<</widget>>
